properties.Name: Southern Silk Route
properties.description:
From 5th cent BC to the 14th cent AD caravans moved along the Slk Roads between the Mediterranenan and China carrying precious materials, artists, and ideas.

For an elaborate historical timeline of Central Asian events see
http://rolfgross.dreamhosters.com/Texts/Eastwest.htm
